全力配合交警部门开展下一步的工作。 夏庆华在蔚来汽车 App 发布声明称，根据受损车辆初步判断，电池包基本完好，具体事故原因仍在调查中。夏庆华称，蔚来汽车方面对罹难用户致以深深地哀悼，对他的家属和好友表示深切慰问。将协助用户家属做好善后工作。蔚来目前正配合有关部门分析事故原因。有需要跟大家同步的信息会及时告知。 蔚来汽车创始人李斌在声明下留言表示，一早听到这个消息，十分难过，哀悼不幸身故的用户已经组织小组帮助善后和事故调查工作。又出事！31 岁蔚来车主自动驾驶车祸去世，曾创多个知名品牌！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-afd8916581cf55c1f1a40981d80b40e4_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "167 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/479842182"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ivc684uOj944mEAMaCDY4OTEyOTk5IK/E4YgGMAA4mQJAEXIJNDc5ODQyMTgyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1629000511.9849236", "card_id": "Q_479536718", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 34}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么三灾给人的压迫感不如三将星？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-810b21079d0cbd1041b52412b79f24f0_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "151 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/479536718"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ivc684uOj944mEAMaCDY4ODQ0OTUxIKKO2YgGMAM4RUAScgk0Nzk1MzY3MTh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1629000511.9854078", "card_id": "Q_479791485", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 32}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2021 LPL 夏季赛的 TES 问题出在哪？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ed377f15654be32c065c52f20ae7e777_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "143 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/479791485"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ivc684uOj944mEAMaCDY4OTAxNzY1IMmb34gGMAA4K0ATcgk0Nzk3OTE0ODV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1629000511.9859345", "card_id":